1
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Step right up and have a look...</font>

2
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time for Yamishibai.</font>

3
00:00:10,610 --> 00:00:17,530
<font face="Times New Roman" size="44" color="#593826"><b>{\an8}<font color="#5e3623"><font color="#5c352c">Theatre of Darkness: Yamishibai</font></font></b></font>

4
00:00:13,360 --> 00:00:17,530
<font face="Times New Roman" size="22" color="#3d2b20"><font color="#2b1f0a">Sleeper Train</font></font>

5
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the story of some women who have 
taken a sleeper train on a vacation...</font>

6
00:00:23,830 --> 00:00:26,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, so this is what it's like!</font>

7
00:00:26,990 --> 00:00:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks more comfortable than I thought.</font>

8
00:00:30,420 --> 00:00:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Staying an extra day and taking the 
sleeper train might be worth it.</font>

9
00:00:37,410 --> 00:00:39,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want to do once we get there?</font>

10
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:44,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I forgot to make sure 
we could check in early...</font>

11
00:00:44,890 --> 00:00:48,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, a free-wheeling vacation where we 
don't plan everything out could be fun.</font>

12
00:00:50,730 --> 00:00:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come in.</font>

13
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to bother you 
while you're relaxing.</font>

14
00:00:55,380 --> 00:01:00,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for riding with us on 
the Evening Star sleeper train.</font>

15
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I check your tickets?</font>

16
00:01:03,580 --> 00:01:06,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sure. Here're both of ours.</font>

17
00:01:06,340 --> 00:01:07,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much.</font>

18
00:01:07,610 --> 00:01:09,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll just check these.</font>

19
00:01:09,740 --> 00:01:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's one thing I need 
to caution you about.</font>

20
00:01:12,090 --> 00:01:15,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will be connecting with another 
car during a stop tonight.</font>

21
00:01:15,550 --> 00:01:16,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Connecting?</font>

22
00:01:16,690 --> 00:01:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. It'll be dangerous,</font>

23
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:23,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we'd like to ask you not to leave 
your car or open your curtains.</font>

24
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't even open the curtains?</font>

25
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:30,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We ask it for your own safety, miss.</font>

26
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:34,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, a lot of tickets 
have gone missing lately.</font>

27
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:37,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be sure to hold on to yours at all times
until you reach your destination.</font>

28
00:01:37,740 --> 00:01:38,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

29
00:01:38,990 --> 00:01:40,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I hope you enjoy your journey.</font>

30
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:44,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"At all times" seems a little extreme.</font>

31
00:01:44,730 --> 00:01:48,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True. I'm gonna go buy some drinks.</font>

32
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that?</font>

33
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Talk about creepy.</font>

34
00:01:55,260 --> 00:01:58,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y'know, over by the part of 
the car that connects...</font>

35
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:02,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And she's asleep. She must've been tired.</font>

36
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:06,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, we need to close the curtains, too.</font>

37
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this the stop he mentioned?</font>

38
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to the bathroom.</font>

39
00:02:16,790 --> 00:02:18,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we're not supposed to leave the car.</font>

40
00:02:18,990 --> 00:02:21,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way. Do you want me to pee in here?</font>

41
00:02:21,570 --> 00:02:22,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unbelievable.</font>

42
00:02:27,010 --> 00:02:32,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the car that connected to us? 
And it's not a sleeper car.</font>

43
00:02:32,230 --> 00:02:34,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, it's super packed.</font>

44
00:02:43,210 --> 00:02:44,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

45
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:47,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't turn on? Is it a power outage?</font>

46
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are these people?!</font>

47
00:02:59,170 --> 00:03:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miwa?!</font>

48
00:03:00,810 --> 00:03:02,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you?!</font>

49
00:03:02,050 --> 00:03:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's me, the conductor. 
I'll need to check your ticket again.</font>

50
00:03:04,340 --> 00:03:08,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget that! My friend... 
I think she was screaming...</font>

51
00:03:08,860 --> 00:03:10,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You let go of yours.</font>

52
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:22,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

53
00:03:22,350 --> 00:03:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{Missing?}</font>

54
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:30,180
<font face="Times New Roman" size="44" color="#593826"><b>{\an8}<font size="34">Theatre of Darkness: Yamishibai</font></b></font>

55
00:03:26,850 --> 00:03:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The end.</font>

